snippet.textDisplay: I ended a 10 year relationship with someone I thought I would have spent the rest of my life with in 2018. I was completely loss, forgotten who I was and still felt like I needed him to feel whole. I hit rock bottom when I went on a family trip to Southeast Asia that year and didn’t realize I displaced all my pain and anger onto my family. That’s when I knew I needed a change. I went into myself and meditated, practiced yoga and journaled/read. I even started working out so I have an Asian booty lol Throughout all of this, I never realized you were going through the same thing until you started your book club and recommended “Life lessons- everything you wished you learned in kindergarten” it was a game changer. It helped me recenter and understand life isn’t always how we planned but because there’s something more for us to discover. You helped me without even knowing you did. I even wrote down what I wanted and deserved from the next guy and promised myself that I wouldn’t settle for less. After 4 months, I ended up going to an event I normally wouldn’t say yes to and met my man. It’s crazy the power of manifestation. Thank you for being the voice that everyone has but so few speak their truth. I don’t think I would have gotten through what I’ve been through until I heard your story.
